The paper also presents some decoupling type theorems, which are related to cryptography and security, making cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) another possible category. The paper also involves some applications in privacy amplification and random coding exponents, which are related to data structures and algorithms, making cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) another possible category.
